sources.title: Johnny Was - Full Movie
sources.description:
A thriller in the vein of 'Lock Stock' and 'The Long Good Friday,' 'Johnny Was' follows former Irish thug Johnny Doyle as he navigates questions of race and morality in an attempt to avoid all-out war with West Indian Yardies in a Brixton safehouse.
